file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: "API"
  version: "1.0.0"
  contact:
    name: Starkina Maria
    email: starkina@surfstudio.ru

paths:
  /feedback/faq:
    get:
      summary: Вопросы и ответы
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "Все ок"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items: 
                  $ref: "models.yaml#/components/schemas/FaqItem"
        default:
          $ref: "../common/errors.yaml#/components/responses/ApiErrorResponse"

Error: parse: paths: /feedback/faq: get: : responses: default: resolve "../common/errors.yaml#/components/responses/ApiErrorResponse" reference: invalid response reference: "../common/errors.yaml#/components/responses/ApiErrorResponse"
